data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. NO FLOOD ZONE HERE! Consumer websites are NOT reflective of recent FEMA change to NO FLOOD ZONE (zone X) for this beautiful home! NEW CONSTRUCTION! Highly upgraded and NEVER LIVED IN! Why wait 10-12 months to build when this brand new, POND VIEW home is ready to be yours today? Welcome to The Hammocks of West Port; a charming master planned community located in booming Port Charlotte, Florida! This new construction home is filled to the brim with numerous upgrades including HURRICANE IMPACT WINDOWS, crown molding throughout, tray ceilings, additional lighting, and more! The primary en-suite bathroom feels like your own private spa with premium bathroom finishes including French door entry, frameless shower door, soaking tub, 'waterfall' ceiling-mounted shower head, large dual vanity, and generous linen closet. Love to cook? Then you'll enjoy spending time in this open concept kitchen with upgraded 42 inch cabinets, soft-close drawers & doors, granite countertops, double door pantry, upgraded appliance package and oversized island with pendant light pre-wires. 2100+ square feet, 4 bedrooms and 3 FULL BATHROOMS ensure that there will be plenty of room for everyone to comfortably enjoy their own space, making this the perfect multi-generational floorplan. The Hammocks enjoys a very reasonable monthly fee which includes landscaping maintenance and irrigation. Located a few short blocks from the Centennial Park Rec Center, Charlotte Regional Sports Park, and Centennial Pool Park & Aquatic Center (which can be joined for a small annual fee, if desired) means you can find swimming, walking trails, pickleball, fitness classes, disc golf, baseball, soccer (and much more!) just moments from your front door! This home is ideally located less than a 10 minute drive to both Murdock Circle AND Cocoplum Plaza... giving you endless access to numerous restaurants, shopping, and conveniences! Call today for your private showing or check out our 3-D INTERACTIVE VIRTUAL TOUR! (One or more photos may be virtually staged)
